data.description: This one and a half story with a circle drive in the west end has great curb appeal! This 3-2-2 has been updated with too many amenities to list. One being, no carpet but rather tile plus the original hardwood floors have been meticulously restored. This home has a huge den along with a formal living room and a bright/airy kitchen that has ample counter space that nicely flows into a formal dining room. The formal living room has cathedral ceilings which also boasts a striking staircase leading up to a loft/balcony, a master bedroom with an updated master bath. The master bedroom actually has two rooms, one currently used an an exercise room and the other as the master bedroom. Both guest bedrooms are a nice size along with a second updated bathroom off of the hall. Very pretty fireplace with a gas starter and beautiful, wooden patio doors which will introduce you to an oversized, fenced backyard with a patio and a workshop for storing the lawn equipment!
